<div class="card mb-3 p-4 border-0">
  <div class="row intro">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <img src="<%= asset_pack_path 'media/images/tang.jpeg'%>" class="img-thumbnail">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <div class="card-body pt-1">
        <h4 class="category card-title mx-0 mt-0">盛唐</h4>
        <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0 text-muted">
          <p>「618年－907年」，享国二百八十九年。当时世界上最强盛的国家之一，声誉远播，疆域辽阔，万国来朝达到鼎盛，后人多称唐人。</p>
        </blockquote>
        <br>
        <h4 class="category card-title mx-0 mt-0">诗坛</h4>
        <div class="d-flex mb-2">
          <blockquote class="flex-grow-1 blockquote mb-0">
            <p class="mb-2">桃花流水窅然去，别有天地非人间。</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer float-right">诗仙 - 李白 <cite title="Source Title">《山中问答》</cite></footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex mb-2">
          <blockquote class="flex-grow-1 blockquote mb-0">
            <p class="mb-2">三顾频烦天下计，两朝开济老臣心。</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer float-right">诗圣 - 杜甫 <cite title="Source Title">《蜀相》</cite></footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex mb-2">
          <blockquote class="flex-grow-1 blockquote mb-0">
            <p class="mb-2">前不见古人，后不见来者。念天地之悠悠，独怆然而涕下。</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer float-right">诗骨 - 陈子昂 <cite title="Source Title">《登幽州台歌》</cite></footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
